  "remarks": "CFi.006 Designation: Former Séléka General. Is a diamond smuggler and a three-star general of the Séléka and close confident of former CAR interim president Michel Djotodia. Physical description: hair colour: black; height: 180cm; belongs to the Fulani ethnic group. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice. CAR diplomatic passport no. D00000898, issued on 11 April 2013, (valid until 10 April 2018).; Listing: Listed on 20 Aug. 2015 (amended 20 Oct. 2015)",
